m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +3 furious brass falcata grants its wielder the ability to cast righteous might {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} once per day as a 9th level cleric.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This is one of the gifts of the royal court master Shaynih'a, who arrived to the Stolen Lands from the foreign land of Vudra in search of her vocation.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This weapon is a +2 keen furious falcata.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Perfect for doing exactly what its name implies.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +2 falcata grants its wearer a +5 morale {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on all {g|Encyclopedia:Persuasion}Persuasion checks{/g}. Whenever the wielder uses Dazzling Display, all affected enemies suffer {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d8{/g} sonic {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.
This +1 falcata grants its wearer a +2 {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g} for all {g|Encyclopedia:TouchAttack}touch attacks{/g}.

This +3 unholy falcata was corrupted by demons. It feeds on fear. Whenever it lands a hit on a shaken or frightened enemy, the target must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 22) or become prone for 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}round{/g} and suffer {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d12{/g} negative {g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}energy damage{/g}.

Whenever the wielder of this +4 cruel bleed falcata is engaged in melee with a single enemy and there are no other enemies in a 15-foot range, the enemy gets a -2 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} on {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g} and {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}saving throws{/g}.
This +5 vicious sacrificial falcata allows its wearer to deal additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}3d6{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}slashing damage{/g} against Medium and smaller enemies on hit.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
